# NexusAI Environment Variables
#
# This project is a monorepo containing a frontend client and backend server.
# Both directories have their own environment configuration files.
#
# Please configure:
# 1. Frontend: Create client/.env from client/.env.example
#    Link: client/.env.example
#
# 2. Backend: Create server/.env from server/.env.example
#    Link: server/.env.example
